### InternLink API Documentation
### Base URL: http://localhost:4000/api

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Login
### Method: POST
### Description: Authenticate user and receive JWT token
### Required Fields: email, password
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Response (200 OK):
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Login successful",
###   "data": {
###     "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
###     "user": {
###       "id": "user-id",
###       "email": "user@example.com",
###       "role": "INTERN" | "PROVIDER"
###     }
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2025-12-29T10:30:00.000Z"
### }

### ============================================
### SIGNUP ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Signup as Intern
### Method: POST
### Description: Register a new intern account
### Required Fields: fullName, email, password, university, major
### Optional Fields: graduationYear
POST http://localhost:4000/api/intern/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "intern@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "university": "MIT",
  "major": "Computer Science",
  "graduationYear": 2025
}

### Response (201 Created):
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Signup successful",
###   "data": {
###     "user": {
###       "id": "user-id",
###       "email": "intern@example.com",
###       "role": "INTERN",
###       "internProfile": {
###         "fullName": "John Doe",
###         "university": "MIT",
###         "major": "Computer Science",
###         "graduationYear": 2025
###       }
###     }
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2025-12-29T10:30:00.000Z"
### }

### Signup as Provider
### Method: POST
### Description: Register a new provider (company) account
### Required Fields: companyName, email, password, industry
### Optional Fields: website
POST http://localhost:4000/api/provider/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Tech Company Inc",
  "email": "company@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "industry": "Technology",
  "website": "https://techcompany.com"
}

### Response (201 Created):
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Signup successful",
###   "data": {
###     "user": {
###       "id": "user-id",
###       "email": "company@example.com",
###       "role": "PROVIDER",
###       "providerProfile": {
###         "companyName": "Tech Company Inc",
###         "industry": "Technology",
###         "website": "https://techcompany.com"
###       }
###     }
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2025-12-29T10:30:00.000Z"
### }

